-- Toyota Says It Isn't Interested in Fiat's Factory, Denying Report by Ansa
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2010-10-13T13:51:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/toyota-says-it-isn-t-interested-in-fiat-s-factory-denying-report-by-ansa.html
Toyota Motor Corp. isn’t interested
in taking over Fiat SpA’s factory in Termini Imerese, denying an
Ansa newswire report saying the Japanese carmaker may have made
an offer.  “It’s totally untrue,” Toyota spokesman Etienne Plas said
by telephone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
